OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave another largely dry
OL,7,Fand fine day. Cloud will tend to
OL,8,Fbubble up around the middle of the day
OL,9,Fwith perhaps the odd shower
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Feeling warm in the
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining fine and dry this
OL,14,Fevening with some late sunshine. Cloud
OL,15,Flikely to increase overnight but
OL,16,Fremaining dry across the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
