OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FStaying largely dry on
OL,6,FWednesday with a mix of cloud and
OL,7,Fspells of sunshine. An isolated shower
OL,8,Fcan't be ruled out but most places
OL,9,Favoiding them. Feeling warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FThe
OL,12,Flargely dry, warm and settled theme
OL,13,Fcontinuing on Thursday and Friday. A
OL,14,Fchange in the weather then expected on
OL,15,FSaturday as a band of rain likely to
OL,16,Fmove in.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
